    {
      "section_id": "para_33",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "An Act to incorporate the Synod of the Diocese of West Malaysia.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_34",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "[Peninsular Malaysia—3 September 1971]",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_35",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "WHEREAS there was constituted and established in Malaysia on   8 \nApril 1970 a Synod of the Diocese of West Malaysia on the authority \nof  the  Archbishop  of  Canterbury  as  the  Metropolitan  having \njurisdiction over the Anglican Church in that territory:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_36",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "AND  WHEREAS  the  Synod  of  the  Diocese  of  West  Malaysia  is \nbeneficially  entitled  to  certain  movable  and  immovable  properties  in \nPeninsular  Malaysia  which  are  at  present  vested  in  the  Secretary  of  the \nSynod of the Diocese of Singapore as incorporated under the Synod of the \nDiocese of Singapore Ordinance 1958 [Ord. 67 of 1958]:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_37",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "AND  WHEREAS  it  is  expedient  to  incorporate  the  Synod  of  the",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_38",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Diocese of West Malaysia and their successors:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_39",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "BE IT ENACTED by the Seri Paduka Baginda Yang di-Pertuan Agong \nwith the advice and consent of the Dewan Negara and Dewan Rakyat in \nParliament assembled, and by the authority of the same, as follows:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_40",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Short title",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_41",
      "heading": "1.   This  Act  may  be  cited  as  the  Synod  of  the  Diocese  of  West \nMalaysia (Incorporation) Act 1971.",
      "content": "1.   This  Act  may  be  cited  as  the  Synod  of  the  Diocese  of  West \nMalaysia (Incorporation) Act 1971.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_42",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Incorporation, etc.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_43",
      "heading": "2.   (1)   The  Synod  of  the  Diocese  of  West  Malaysia,  and  its",
      "content": "2.   (1)   The  Synod  of  the  Diocese  of  West  Malaysia,  and  its",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_44",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6                                 Laws of Malaysia",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_45",
      "heading": "ACT 36",
      "content": "ACT 36",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_46",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "successors  shall  be  a  body  corporate  and  shall  have  perpetual \nsuccession  under  the  name  “The  Synod  of  the  Diocese  of  West \nMalaysia”  hereinafter  called  the  Corporation  and  shall  be  the \ngoverning body of the Anglican Church in Peninsular Malaysia.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_47",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  The  Corporation  may  enter  into  contracts,  and  may  acquire, \npurchase,  take,  hold  and  enjoy  movable  and  immovable  property  of \nevery description and may convey, transfer, assign, surrender and yield \nup, charge, mortgage, demise, reassign or otherwise dispose of, or deal \nwith, any movable or immovable property vested in the Corporation \nand may lend or borrow money upon such terms as to  the Standing \nCommittee  of  the  Corporation,  hereafter  referred  to  as  the  Standing \nCommittee, may seem fit, and the minutes of the Standing Committee \nshall be sufficient evidence of such terms.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_48",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3)  The Corporation may sue and be sued in respect of its property \nand otherwise in all courts of justice and in all matters and suits.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_49",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Common seal of Corporation, etc.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_50",
      "heading": "3.  (1) The Corporation shall have a common seal, and such seal may \nfrom time to time be broken, changed, altered and made anew as to the \nStanding Committee seems fit.",
      "content": "3.  (1) The Corporation shall have a common seal, and such seal may \nfrom time to time be broken, changed, altered and made anew as to the \nStanding Committee seems fit.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_51",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)  The seal of the Corporation shall not be affixed to any deed, \ndocument or other instrument except by authority of a resolution of the \nStanding  Committee  and  in  the  presence  of  two  members  of  the \nStanding Committee one of whom shall be the Bishop of the Diocese \nof West Malaysia or the Vicar-General appointed by the Bishop or by \nthe Archbishop of the Province of the Anglican Church in South-east \nAsia during a vacancy in the See of West Malaysia or the Chancellor, \nTreasurer, or Secretary of the Corporation.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_52",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3)  All deeds, documents and other instruments requiring the seal \nof the Corporation shall be sealed with the seal of the Corporation \nand  shall  also  be  signed  by  the  two  witnesses  referred  to  in \nsubsection (2).",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_53",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Synod of the Diocese of West Malaysia  \n(Incorporation)",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_54",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "7",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_55",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(4)    Such signing shall be sufficient evidence that the said seal was \nduly and properly affixed and that the said seal is the lawful seal of the \nCorporation.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_56",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(5)    A  certificate  purporting  to  be  signed  by  the  Bishop  of  the \nDiocese  of  West  Malaysia  or  in  his  absence  the  Vicar-General \nappointed by the Bishop or by the Archbishop of the Province of the \nAnglican  Church  in  South-east  Asia  during  a  vacancy  in  the  See  of \nWest Malaysia shall be sufficient evidence as to the persons who from \ntime to time are members of the Standing Committee and who are the \nChancellor, Treasurer and Secretary of the Corporation.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_57",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Transfer of certain properties",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_58",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "4.  (1)  The  Secretary  of  the  Synod  of  the  Diocese  of  Singapore  as \nincorporated  under  the  Synod  of  the  Diocese  of  Singapore  Ordinance \n1958 in whom is vested all movable and immovable property situated in \nPeninsular Malaysia belonging to the Corporation immediately before the \ncommencement of this Act is hereby divested of all such movable and \nimmovable property and all estates, rights and interests therein.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_59",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2)   All movable and immovable property referred to in subsection (1) \nand  all  estates,  rights  and  interests  therein  are  hereby  vested  in  the \nCorporation for the respective estates, rights  and interests for  which \nthe same are held  and  the Corporation shall have full power to  deal \nwith the said property as provided in subsection 2(2).",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_60",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3)   The appropriate Land Administrator or Registrar of Titles, as \nthe case may be, shall substitute the name of the Corporation in place \nof that of the registered holder in the case of any registered interest in \nimmovable  property  in  Peninsular  Malaysia  formerly  vested  in  the \nSecretary of the Synod of the Diocese of Singapore.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_61",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Repeal",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_62",
      "heading": "5.  The Synod of the Diocese of Singapore Ordinance 1958 is hereby \nrepealed.",
      "content": "5.  The Synod of the Diocese of Singapore Ordinance 1958 is hereby \nrepealed.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
